high_descs: Go straight along the counters to the space between the stove and the sink.
Pick up a peach from the counter next to the sink.
Place the peach on the same sink but in between the mug and the bowl.
anns.task_desc: Place a peach on a kitchen counter next to a sink.

high_descs: Turn around and move towards the sink
Pick the peach from the sink top
Turn around and move towards the other end of the  sink
place the peach on the sink top
anns.task_desc: place the peach on the sink top on the other end

high_descs: See around and to straight, then turn left towards the sink counter top.
Pick up the peach in front of the bowl from the sink counter top.
Turn right and walk, then turn left and walk towards the fridge, then turn left to another side of the sink counter top.
Put the peach in between the bowl and mug on the sink counter top.
anns.task_desc: Put a peach on the sink counter top.
